{"tid":2278294,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼發炮：阿古路太肥 獲加太蠢","createTime":"2020-11-09T05:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T10:20:32.000Z","uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6dd55f01a6ad092f7ef9dd4d66b5408472dbb7","tid":2278294,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"曼聯名宿堅尼狠批曼城雙星阿古路、卡爾獲加，更指前者傷癒後身形走樣。<br />\n<br />\n堅尼（Roy Keane）現在為英國天空體育擔任評述員，風格與球員時代一樣火爆，經常不留情地炮轟球員，在曼城主場以1:1逼和利物浦的大戰也不例外。 「當阿古路復出後，他看來超重了，天知道他要穿甚麼尺寸的波褲，他看來真的很重，非常重！」堅尼表示。 <br />\n<br />\n除了阿古路之外，堅尼還狠批在13分鐘失掉12碼的右閘卡爾獲加：「沙迪奧文尼博得12碼，全因面對的獲加是一名蠢材。」 「大家都告訴我獲加有多好，我不同意。他已經30歲，而且是英格蘭國腳，但就像車禍一樣，一直犯下類似的錯誤，一直被判罰。」49歲的堅尼續說。"},{"pid":"4fa342a80273c9fbd21510ffc6765d1a485683d2","tid":2278294,"uid":311309,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"所有明叔都係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0eec505b608a5958145dae1578a459817b2fbb","tid":2278294,"uid":150109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"Walker 今季都輸咗3 4球 penalty<br />\n仲要唔係手球輸 唔知佢諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b3d9cedd114b9a46fc1122e8838f0870b81912","tid":2278294,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"KDB 12碼唔中龍唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c171832330c9448f2e90874155a7a8296d3905","tid":2278294,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"牙路呢d叫bulk 不過我諗你個廢老太脫節<br />\n唔知咩叫bulk <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de961343ae2031be575f570e4307e6ce1b1d69c3","tid":2278294,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0eec505b608a5958145dae1578a459817b2fbb","tid":2278294,"uid":150109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"Walke